      "content": "i dont even know why im still doing this. i did everything i could for him. i stayed up every night, i skipped meals, i gave up my whole life... and it didnt even matter. he's gone and it feels like all that effort was just for nothing. i'm just so tired. i'm so incredibly tired of everything.",
